This paper is about image classification and feature learning, which are both topics within computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE) in the proposed approach. Additionally, the paper mentions object categorization (cs.AI) and face recognition (cs.MM) as specific applications of their method.
